Show HN: NYT Spelling Bee Year in Review
text:
Hey!

As a super-fan of the NYT Spelling Bee, I'm excited to share this year's "Year In Review," an in-depth analysis of the words and trends we saw throughout the year.

If you're also a fan of the Spelling Bee, or just want to check out Hex, the tool used for the analysis and data viz, it's worth a look.

Hope y'all enjoy.
